<header>
  <h1><img
      src="https://images.vexels.com/media/users/3/152676/isolated/lists/4901900ec6cd623e843598a78d23eefa-triple-cheeseburger-icon.png"
      alt="burger"></h1>
  <h1>EAT-DA-BURGER!</h1>
  <h2><i>Order & Devour Your Favorite Burgers!</i></h2>
  <p>"I was at a restaurant, I saw a guy wearing a leather jacket at the same time he was eating a hamburger and
    drinking a glass of milk. I said, "Dude, you are a cow. The metamorphosis is complete. Don't fall asleep, or I will
    tip you over." ~ Mitch Hedberg</p>

</header>

<div class="container" style="text-align: -webkit-center; padding-top: 2%">
  <div class="row mb-3" style="justify-content: center">
    <div class="tobedevoured col-sm-4">
      <h5 class="text-center py-1">BURGERS TO BE POUNDED!</h5>

      {{#each burgers}}
      {{#unless devoured}}
      {{> burgers/burger-block}}
      {{/unless}}
      {{/each}}
    </div>

    <div class="toeat col-sm-4">
      <h5 class="text-center py-1">BURGERS YOU ANNIHALATED!</h5>
      <ul class="burgers-devoured">
        {{#each burgers}}
        {{#if devoured}}
        {{> burgers/burger-block}}
        {{/if}}
        {{/each}}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="toadd col-sm-4">
    <h5 class="text-center py-1">ADD YOUR BURGER</h5>
    <form class="create-form mx-auto">
      <div class="form-group">
        <input class="mx-auto d-block" placeholder="Enter a Burger Name" type="text" id="ca" name="name">
        <label for="ca"></label>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group1">
        <label for="devoured">Check one of the lists to add your new BURGER</label><br>
        <input type="radio" name="devoured" value="1" checked> ADD TO THE "BURGERS TO BE POUNDED" LIST!<br>
        <input type="radio" name="devoured" value="0"> ADD TO THE "DEVOURED" LIST!
      </div>
      <input class="btn btn-primary" type="submit" value="Submit">
  </div>
</div>

<div class="footer">
  <p>"I was at a restaurant, I saw a guy wearing a leather jacket at the same time he was eating a hamburger and
    drinking a glass of milk. I said "Dude, you are a cow. The metamorphosis is complete. Don't fall asleep, or I will
    tip you over." ~ Mitch Hedberg</p>
</div>